Music star, Chibuzor Oji, popularly known as Faze is bereaved. The artiste and entrepreneur lost his twin sister on Monday. In a post on Instagram, Faze disclosed that she passed away 48 hours to their birthday. “It’s a sad day. My Twin sister has left me just two days to our birthday”, he wrote. “We the Oji family take strength in knowing that she’ll never have to deal with this world’s problems anymore. We know she’s in a better place now.” His fans and colleagues are paying tribute to the deceased. Faze was a member of the Plantashun Boyz, along with Blackface and TuFace. The trio went separate ways in 2004 to pursue solo careers